text: Zoe Konstantopoulou (; born 8 December 1976) is a Greek lawyer and politician. She was President of the Hellenic Parliament in 2015. She was elected to the post on 6 February 2015 with the record number of 235 out of 300 votes. Since 2016 she is President of the political party Course of Freedom. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Politicians from Athens Category:Living people Category:Greek lawyers Category:Speakers of the Hellenic Parliament
